Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:39.36,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}My love and I did meet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:46.68,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}She passed the salley gardens
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:53.24,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}With little snow-white feet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:22:00.38,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}She bid me take love easy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.99,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}As the leaves grow on the tree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:14.72,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}But I,being young and foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:21.56,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}With her did not agree
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:42.43,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}But I  was young and foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:51.60,ED_ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000}{\blur0.65\shad1}{be1}And now I am full of tears
